    <header>
        <h1>Make Money Online in 2024</h1>
    </header>
    
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>1. Freelancing</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Upwork:</strong> A comprehensive platform for freelancers across various fields. It offers a range of projects from short-term to long-term contracts.
                    <br><a href="https://www.upwork.com/?referral=your-referral-link">Sign up for Upwork</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Fiverr:</strong> Ideal for offering specific services or "gigs" starting at $5. It covers a broad spectrum of categories and allows you to showcase your expertise.
                    <br><a href="https://www.fiverr.com/?referral=your-referral-link">Join Fiverr</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Toptal:</strong> A selective network connecting top freelancers with high-end clients. Best for experienced professionals in software development, design, and finance.
                    <br><a href="https://www.toptal.com/?referral=your-referral-link">Apply to Toptal</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Freelancer:</strong> Offers a wide variety of projects and contests. It’s a great platform to start and build your freelancing career.
                    <br><a href="https://www.freelancer.com/?referral=your-referral-link">Get started on Freelancer</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>Skills:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Writing:</strong> Content creation, copywriting, editing, and proofreading.</li>
                <li><strong>Graphic Design:</strong> Creating visuals for branding, marketing materials, and digital content.</li>
                <li><strong>Web Development:</strong> Building and maintaining websites, web applications, and providing technical support.</li>
                <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> Digital marketing, SEO, social media management, and campaign strategy.</li>
                <li><strong>Virtual Assistance:</strong> Administrative tasks, email management, scheduling, and customer support.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>Freelancing can be a rewarding career choice, offering the flexibility to work from anywhere and the opportunity to earn a substantial income by leveraging your skills. Whether you’re looking to supplement your income or build a full-time business, these platforms provide the resources and connections to help you succeed.</p>
            
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>2. Content Creation</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> YouTube, Twitch, TikTok, Instagram, Medium</p>
            <p><strong>Methods:</strong> Ad revenue, sponsorships, affiliate marketing, fan donations (Patreon, Ko-fi)</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>3. Online Teaching and Tutoring</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Udemy, Teachable, Coursera, VIPKid</p>
            <p><strong>Skills:</strong> Academic subjects, professional skills, hobbies</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>4. E-commerce</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Shopify, Etsy, Amazon FBA, eBay</p>
            <p><strong>Methods:</strong> Selling physical products, dropshipping, print on demand</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>5. Investing and Trading</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Robinhood, eToro, Coinbase, Binance</p>
            <p><strong>Assets:</strong> Stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, NFTs</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>6. Remote Work</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> LinkedIn, We Work Remotely, Remote.co</p>
            <p><strong>Fields:</strong> IT, marketing, customer service, project management</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>7. Blogging and Affiliate Marketing</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> WordPress, Blogger, Squarespace</p>
            <p><strong>Methods:</strong> Affiliate links, sponsored posts, ad revenue</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>8. Online Surveys and Market Research</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Swagbucks, Survey Junkie, Vindale Research</p>
            <p><strong>Methods:</strong> Completing surveys, testing products, watching videos</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>9. Virtual Assistance</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Belay, Time Etc, Fancy Hands</p>
            <p><strong>Tasks:</strong> Administrative support, email management, scheduling</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>10. Selling Digital Products</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Gumroad, Sellfy, Etsy (digital)</p>
            <p><strong>Products:</strong> E-books, printables, software, music, courses</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>11. Membership Sites and Subscription Services</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Patreon, Substack, OnlyFans</p>
            <p><strong>Content:</strong> Exclusive articles, videos, podcasts, community access</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>12. Online Coaching and Consulting</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Clarity.fm, Coach.me, Zoom</p>
            <p><strong>Fields:</strong> Business, life, fitness, mental health</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>13. Social Media Management</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Hootsuite, Buffer, SocialBee</p>
            <p><strong>Clients:</strong> Small businesses, influencers, brands</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>14. App and Software Development</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> App Store, Google Play, GitHub (for open-source monetization)</p>
            <p><strong>Methods:</strong> Selling apps, in-app purchases, subscriptions</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>15. Renting and Sharing Economy</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Airbnb, Turo, RentMyEquipment</p>
            <p><strong>Methods:</strong> Renting out property, vehicles, equipment</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>16. Online Art and Craft Sales</h2>
            <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> DeviantArt, Redbubble, Society6</p>
            <p><strong>Products:</strong> Art prints, custom designs, handmade crafts</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Tips for Success</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Leverage Social Media:</strong> Build a strong online presence to promote your services or products.</li>
                <li><strong>Continuous Learning:</strong> Stay updated with industry trends and improve your skills.</li>
                <li><strong>Networking:</strong> Join online communities and forums to connect with potential clients and collaborators.</li>
                <li><strong>Quality Over Quantity:</strong> Focus on delivering high-quality products or services to build a loyal customer base.</li>
                <li><strong>Diversification:</strong> Don’t rely on a single income stream; diversify your methods to ensure steady income.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
